  "subject": "Add MaxRAMPercentage=50% JVM default to Dockerfile",
  "commit_message": "Add MaxRAMPercentage=50% JVM default to Dockerfile\n\nWithout explicit MaxRAMPercentage, the JVM defaults to 25% of\ncontainer memory for heap while non-heap grows unconstrained.\nSetting 50% provides a balanced default that works with the\nreduced container limits from OOM-3391.\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4353\nChange-Id: I2ff4bb5b0d48644099402aeb6d448de7b0067f9b\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
